note: Grace Health is dedicated to keeping our community healthy. When you contribute to Grace Health, you help keep it healthy. Your financial support helps us bridge the gap between the actual cost of providing quality health care services, and the income Grace Health receives from grants and fee payments. Most importantly, your support allows us to honor our commitment to keep our services affordable and accessible for everyone in our community who needs us.
